{"tid":2227583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7.21 後矢志不做打機「港豬」　小六生搞天水圍社區關注組　課後活動是「做區」","createTime":"2020-10-03T01:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T04:06:17.000Z","uid":271829,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"35c1a3e7cdb591fd9e91e348ce7d1c4b0a264580","tid":2227583,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T01:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/gangagang05_YXnj0_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fgangagang05_YXnj0_1200x0.png&h=29230f54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天水圍社區關注組創辦人王繼祖面無懼色，要求菜檔職員整理行人路的發泡膠箱。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n「為民請命，堅持到底！」聽到這個口號，你或會以為是議員的宣傳字句，不過這其實是出自幾名一臉稚氣的小朋友口中。3 個月前，這幾個平均年齡只得 13 歲的小朋友成立「天水圍社區關注組」（下稱關注組），他們每周巡區、又向街坊派口罩，十足十區議員的工作。他們說：「因為鍾意呢個社區，所以先想呢個社區變得更好。」 地區工作從來不是大人的專利。<br />\n九月尾，中小學恢復面授課堂首日，「天水圍社區關注組」創辦人王繼祖下課後，午飯還沒來得及吃，便立即換上便服，落樓巡區。關注組成立 3 個月，以幫助天水圍街坊為己任，曾成功爭取領展更換天端商場破裂地板。現時，他們首要關注天一商場地下菜檔的衛生問題。<br />\n「唔該，呢個發泡膠箱，我想同你講，可唔可以執番佢呀？阻住路人同埋會有衛生問題。」只得小六的王繼祖面對菜檔職員，毫不畏懼，即使對方無動於衷，仍窮追猛打，職員最終哭笑不得，只好將堆積放在石壆上的雜物拿走。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/images/7-21-後矢志不做打機-港豬-小六生搞天水圍社區關注組-課後活動是-做區/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fimages%2F7-21-%E5%BE%8C%E7%9F%A2%E5%BF%97%E4%B8%8D%E5%81%9A%E6%89%93%E6%A9%9F-%E6%B8%AF%E8%B1%AC-%E5%B0%8F%E5%85%AD%E7%94%9F%E6%90%9E%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%B4%E5%9C%8D%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E7%B5%84-%E8%AA%B2%E5%BE%8C%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%98%AF-%E5%81%9A%E5%8D%80%2F&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmcbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=f2c5cc67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fimages%2F7-21-%E5%BE%8C%E7%9F%A2%E5%BF%97%E4%B8%8D%E5%81%9A%E6%89%93%E6%A9%9F-%E6%B8%AF%E8%B1%AC-%E5%B0%8F%E5%85%AD%E7%94%9F%E6%90%9E%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%B4%E5%9C%8D%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E7%B5%84-%E8%AA%B2%E5%BE%8C%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%98%AF-%E5%81%9A%E5%8D%80%2F&h=78a7686d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/images/7-21-後矢志不做打機-港豬-小六生搞天水圍社區關注組-課後活動是-做區/</a>"},{"pid":"2bf14031c583cc97e6fb39b44fe27f9deb4b7660","tid":2227583,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T02:02:34.000Z","msg":"Good"},{"pid":"10e9806e75f06d7691dc7e5dad8ea7a75f996a1c","tid":2227583,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T02:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52e16e5f9ff498ccfb26456f5747cce5ed548ce","tid":2227583,"uid":106800,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T02:08:10.000Z","msg":"真係有時驚佢既天真會出事"},{"pid":"23bfc647d189dffd2e814c9c5c53d61e7c4f096a","tid":2227583,"uid":93036,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T02:08:39.000Z","msg":"運動既正面影響係令好多年輕一代覺醒進化"},{"pid":"4b43b183e6f2af35acb12c9b64b1b6e4656664fd","tid":2227583,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T02:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80b5617bb43e7c34220f69d84f77a150c1dd4fd","tid":2227583,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T02:12:36.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bbf1e2cdf4cd521d9ce0d662230bcc6308a47ee","tid":2227583,"uid":86673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T02:13:48.000Z","msg":"巧可愛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93cd17764fe2d00231e9ac04aa45157cbd2ce5dc","tid":2227583,"uid":74728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T02:15:21.000Z","msg":"好事嚟"},{"pid":"5360386e04ecac1063139c6c42313606856117e4","tid":2227583,